page.title: 16lifestyles - Denny pupil
page.content: My day starts at 7.50am. I have{cereal or{grapefruit}for my{breakfast.}After that I go into the bathroom to clean my teeth and wash. At 8.25.I leave home and school starts at 9.00. I have English first and at 10.15.I have milk and then it is playtime. After that I do Computation and Maths but on Friday I have a recorder lesson.At 12.15 I go to the dinner hall. I usually bring a packed lunch but sometimes I have a school lunch. School starts again at 1.15. I may have Environmental Studies or R.E..After our last playtime I have another lesson and then I leave school at 3.30. I have dinner at 5.00. On Tuesdays I go to the Brownies but on other days I watch T.V. Later I have supper and go to bed at about 9.00p.m. At weekends I often go with my family for picnics in the country in Summer. {St.Andrews}is my favourite treat.
